OL,6,FA spokesperson for Number 10 said: "We
OL,7,Fhave listened to MPs who support the
OL,8,Fprinciple of reform but are worried
OL,9,Fabout the pace of change for those
OL,10,Falready supported by the system.
OL,12,F"This package will preserve the social
OL,13,Fsecurity system for those who need it
OL,14,Fby putting it on a sustainable
OL,15,Ffooting, provide dignity for those
OL,16,Funable to work, supports those who can
OL,17,Fand reduce anxiety for those currently
OL,18,Fin the system.
