OL,6,F"We will ensure that all of those
OL,7,Fcurrently receiving PIP will stay
OL,8,Fwithin the current system. The new
OL,9,Feligibility requirements will be
OL,10,Fimplemented from November 2026 for new
OL,11,Fclaims only.
OL,13,F"Secondly, we will adjust the pathway
OL,14,Fof Universal Credit payment rates to
OL,15,Fmake sure all existing recipients of
OL,16,Fthe UC health element ` and any new
OL,17,Fclaimant meeting the severe conditions
OL,18,Fcriteria ` have their incomes fully
OL,19,Fprotected in real terms."
