OL,6,FShe said a ministerial review would
OL,7,Fensure the benefit is "fair and fit
OL,8,Ffor the future" and will be a
OL,9,F"coproduction" with disabled people,
OL,10,Forganisations which represent them and
OL,11,FMPs.
OL,13,F"These important reforms are rooted in
OL,14,FLabour values, and we want to get them
OL,15,Fright," she said.
OL,17,FThe change in Pip payments would
OL,18,Fprotect some 370,000 existing
OL,19,Fclaimants who were expected to lose
OL,20,Fout following reassessment.
