OL,6,FIf the legislation clears its first
OL,7,Fhurdle on Tuesday, it will then face a
OL,8,Ffew hours' examination by all MPs the
OL,9,Ffollowing week ` rather than days or
OL,10,Fweeks in front of a committee tasked
OL,11,Fwith looking at the Bill.
