OL,6,FSpeaking in the Commons on Wednesday,
OL,7,FSir Keir told MPs he wanted the
OL,8,Freforms to reflect "Labour values of
OL,9,Ffairness" and that discussions about
OL,10,Fthe changes would continue over the
OL,11,Fcoming days.
OL,13,FHe insisted there was "consensus
OL,14,Facross the House on the urgent need
OL,15,Ffor reform" of the "broken" welfare
OL,16,Fsystem.
OL,18,F"I know colleagues across the House
OL,19,Fare eager to start fixing that, and so
OL,20,Fam I, and that all colleagues want to
OL,21,Fget this right, and so do I," he said.
