OL,6,FHead of campaigns at the charity,
OL,7,FCharlotte Gill, said: "We urge MPs not
OL,8,Fto be swayed by these last-ditch
OL,9,Fattempts to force through a harmful
OL,10,FBill with supposed concessions.
OL,12,F"The only way to avoid a catastrophe
OL,13,Ftoday and in the future is to stop the
OL,14,Fcuts altogether by halting the Bill in
OL,15,Fits tracks."
OL,17,FThe Tories described concessions as
OL,18,F"the latest in a growing list of
OL,19,Fscreeching U-turns" from the
